headline: REV Group, TPI Composites, AeroVironment, nLIGHT, and Axon Shares Plummet, What You Need To Know

headline: Axon (AXON): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Axon currently trades at $792 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 878% since August 2020, blowing past the S&P 500’s 90.8% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 33.5% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
